<h2 id="expressions">Expressions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>When she awoke one morning, she saw him seeing a button on his shirt in the darkness, and she hurried to do it for him before he could say the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="ritual phrase"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(礼仪性词语)</code></b> about needing two wives.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>On the other hand, the only thing she needed from him was that he <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="cup a pain in her back"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(给她拔火罐来消除背痛)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>The dream of other voyages with Florentino Ariza <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="appeared on the horizon"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(浮现在地平线上)</code></b>: mad voyages, free of trunks, free of social commitments: voyages of love.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Holding each other very close, the Captain and Zenaida danced the first boleros that were just beginning to <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="break hearts"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(伤心)</code></b> in those days.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Florentino Ariza <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="dared to"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(大胆做某事)</code></b> suggest to Fermina Daza that they dance their private waltz, but she refused. Nevertheless she <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="kept time with her head and her heels"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(用脑袋和鞋跟打着拍子)</code></b> all night, and there was even a moment when she danced sitting down without realizing it, while the Captain merged with his young wild woman in the shadows of the bolero.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>That night, as a personal contribution to the revelry, Fermina Daza went down to the galley amid the ovations of the crew and prepared a dish for everyone that she created and that Florentino Ariza <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="christened"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(取名为)</code></b> Eggplant al Amor.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>She <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="suffered an attack of laughing"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(突然大笑起来)</code></b> until she cried, which alarmed everyone.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

